title: #92Noon! Cronin/Talkers/BirkBit/Softy
description: ESPN's Courtney Cronin is in studio for the first hour, Matt Birk's weekly spot to start the final hour, and 950KJR's Dave "Softy" Mahler offers the Seahawks perspective from out west to wrap the show.
